  Do you have a business idea that could shape the future of the Arctic? This contest invites young entrepreneurs and startups from around the world to pitch their Arctic-related business ideas at the prestigious High North Dialogue conference in Bodø, Norway. This is your chance to present your vision to leading Arctic experts, investors, and policymakers – and compete for prizes totalling 70,000 NOK.
